title: UFC 238
description: A UFC championship doubleheader will headline the Octagon's return to the Windy City. In the main event, flyweight champion Henry Cejudo will attempt to follow up a stunning first-round knockout victory in his last performance when he battles Brazilian finisher Marlon Moraes for the vacant UFC bantamweight crown. Plus, striking specialist Valentina Shevchenko defends her flyweight title for the first time against Ohio's Jessica "Evil" Eye, who is undefeated since returning to 125 pounds.

The Show. will visit Chicago on Friday, June 21 at United Center.
